msgid "# Qwen3-ASR-1.7B"
msgstr "# Qwen3-ASR-1.7B"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"The released Qwen3-ASR-1.7B is a lightweight, high-performance automatic "
"speech recognition (ASR) model developed by the Qwen Team. It delivers "
"industry-leading recognition accuracy across Chinese/English multi-scene "
"speech, Chinese dialects, multilingual and singing voice scenarios, with "
"native support for long audio and streaming inference, and deep optimization"
" for Ascend NPU hardware."
msgstr ""
"发布的Qwen3-ASR-1.7B是由Qwen团队开发的轻量级高性能自动语音识别（ASR）模型。它在中英文多场景语音、中文方言、多语言及唱歌场景中均提供行业领先的识别精度，原生支持长音频和流式推理，并针对Ascend"
" NPU硬件进行了深度优化。"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-"
"node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点部署、精度和性能评估。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"`Qwen3-ASR-1.7B`(BF16 version): requires 1 Ascend 910B (with 1 x 64G NPUs)."
msgstr "`Qwen3-ASR-1.7B`（BF16版本）：需要1个Ascend 910B（配备1 x 64G NPU）。"

msgid ""
"`Qwen3-ASR-1.7B`(BF16 version): requires 1 Ascend 310P (with 1 x 48G NPUs).\n"
"[Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-1.7B)."
msgstr ""
"`Qwen3-ASR-1.7B`（BF16版本）：需要1个Ascend 310P（配备1 x 48G NPU）。\n"
"[下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-1.7B)。"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享目录，例如 `/root/.cache/`。"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid "`Qwen3-ASR-1.7B` is supported in `vllm-ascend`."
msgstr "`vllm-ascend` 支持 `Qwen3-ASR-1.7B`。"

msgid ""
"You can use our official docker image to run `Qwen3-ASR-1.7B` directly."
msgstr "您可以直接使用我们的官方Docker镜像运行 `Qwen3-ASR-1.7B`。"

msgid ""
"In addition, if you don't want to use the docker image as above, you can "
"also build all from source:"
msgstr "此外，如果您不想使用上述Docker镜像，也可以从源码构建所有内容："

msgid ""
"- Install `vllm-ascend` from source, refer to "
"[installation](../../installation.md)."
msgstr "- 从源码安装 `vllm-ascend`，请参考[安装指南](../../installation.md)。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Atlas 300I A2 2UP"
msgstr "### Atlas 300I A2 2UP"

msgid "### Atlas 300I DUO"
msgstr "### Atlas 300I DUO"

msgid "## Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 功能验证"

msgid ""
"Once your server is started, you can query the model with input prompts:"
msgstr "服务器启动后，您可以使用输入提示查询模型："

msgid "## Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr "## 精度评估"

msgid ""
"After all samples were processed, transcription quality was measured using:"
msgstr "处理完所有样本后，使用以下指标衡量转录质量："

msgid ""
"- WER (Word Error Rate) for word-level recognition accuracy\n"
"- CER (Character Error Rate) for character-level recognition accuracy"
msgstr ""
"- WER（词错误率）用于词级识别精度\n"
"- CER（字符错误率）用于字符级识别精度"

msgid "### Remarks"
msgstr "### 备注"

msgid ""
"This result reflects end-to-end serving performance, including audio "
"preprocessing, request construction, API communication, inference, and "
"response parsing. Actual performance may vary depending on hardware, "
"concurrency, audio length, and deployment configuration."
msgstr "该结果反映了端到端服务性能，包括音频预处理、请求构建、API通信、推理和响应解析。实际性能可能因硬件、并发数、音频长度和部署配置而异。"

msgid ""
"Further benchmarking is recommended for latency distribution, concurrent "
"throughput, long-audio scenarios, and system resource utilization."
msgstr "建议进一步对延迟分布、并发吞吐量、长音频场景和系统资源利用率进行基准测试。"
